metadata.name: The Monk
metadata.description:
A journey of a thousand miles must begins with a single step. When the mind is still, the whole Universe surrenders. The surrender is a natural habit of Universe, when life begins... Life is a series of natural and spontaneous changes. It is in constant change. Don't resist them - that only creates sorrow.

4096 x 4096 264 DPI
